Key Match Events: Trae Young hit a game-winning half-court buzzer-beater to secure a 124-121 victory for the Atlanta Hawks.
Trae Young posted 24 points, two rebounds, and 20 assists.
Collin Sexton tied the game with a three-pointer before Trae Young's game-winner.
Lauri Markkanen scored a game-high 35 points on 11-21 shooting from the field and 8-15 from three.
